{"tid":574413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經前綜合症","createTime":"2018-02-27T11:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T09:57:43.000Z","uid":160660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c984a37bb3c9f41a3acbc6ecae08110d84b19d4c","tid":574413,"uid":160660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"經前緊張綜合症有甚麽症狀？<br />\n<br />\n與經前緊張綜合症有關的症狀，可多達150種，常見的如下：<br />\n<br />\n生理症症狀：<br />\n<br />\n乳房脹痛／觸痛<br />\n手腳腫脹／腫脹感<br />\n體重增加<br />\n頭痛<br />\n困倦及全身無力<br />\n<br />\n心理及行為上的症狀：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">情緒不穩</span>、煩躁易怒<br />\n精神不集中<br />\n健忘<br />\n感覺情緒／反應衝動<br />\n睡眠紊亂、失眠或嗜睡<br />\n食慾變化、胃口改變（嗜高糖、高脂肪的食物）<br />\n<br />\n個個月都咁 好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f5379998fad64a0164ed1b7a9006d3f1878867","tid":574413,"uid":1067,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔做運動<br />\n作息不定時<br />\n食生冷野<br />\n<br />\n多數女仔都係咁跟住日日話自已M痛好慘吞pop唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae5667eda56a0f8aaed2e5ad32edbb3464da939","tid":574413,"uid":160660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8f5379998fad64a0164ed1b7a9006d3f1878867","tid":574413,"uid":1067,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔做運動<br />\n作息不定時<br />\n食生冷野<br />\n<br />\n多數女仔都係咁跟住日日話自已M痛好慘吞pop唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"m痛真係好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  生不如死"},{"pid":"01884fa01c650a0076370d81fad4fca511165a3a","tid":574413,"uid":60937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cae5667eda56a0f8aaed2e5ad32edbb3464da939","tid":574413,"uid":160660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f